DynamicTimeWarping.Match  
MLFeatureExtractor A Feature Extractor looks at each MLObservation in a problem instance and does "something" - typically creating a derived feature, such as computing the distance between two other features that represent positions.
MLModel An RBB ML Model is an RBB populated with the necessary information to create and parameterize a predictive model.
MLObservation An MLObservation is an ordered list of named Features at a moment in time.
MLObservation.GroupFeature  
MLObservation.Metadata Metadata captures information about the metadata in a sequence of Observation.
MLObservationSequence Evaluating a problem generates a sequence of Observations.
MLOnline A problem definition specifies a type of "problem", which is a co-occurrence of events that match a pattern (an array of tagsets) The problem definition monitors Events as they are created and detects specified co-occurrences which are instantiated as Problem Instances.
